item.title: CVE-2023-4238|2024-08-02T07:24:04.168Z -- unknown -- prevent%20files%20%2F%20folders%20access
item.description: The Prevent files / folders access WordPress plugin before 2.5.2 does not validate files to be uploaded, which could allow attackers to upload arbitrary files such as PHP on the server.
